    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Combine the <strong>ground cumin</strong>,<strong> ground coriander</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (cooking for kids? Skip the chilli!), 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> on a plate</p><p>Mix all the spices together – this is your <strong>fajita seasoning</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
