    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed the<strong> red pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips (as finely as you can!)</p><p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
